snippet.title: Hanging With Friends Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Hanging With Friends for free: http://bit.ly/iUsb6T

Hanging With Friends, the new game from the creative geniuses behind Words With Friends, is a brand new twist to the classic game of hangman that adds creativity, strategy and fun for all ages. Build mystery words to stump, amuse or impress your friends, but be prepared to flex those brain muscles as you decipher the words they send back to you.

http://www.hangingwithfriends.com
